items.title: PepsiCo earnings beat estimates, but demand for drinks and snacks drops in North America
items.description: PepsiCo's earnings topped Wall Street's estimates, but the company's revenue missed expectations, as drink and snack demand fell in North America.

items.title: PayPal reports fourth-quarter earnings beat as growth picks up at Venmo
items.description: PayPal reported better-than-expected fourth-quarter earnings and revenue in its quarterly report on Tuesday.

items.title: Merck's 2025 revenue outlook falls short as it pauses Gardasil vaccine shipments to China
items.description: Merck's full-year 2025 revenue guidance fell short of what some analysts were expecting, at a range of $64.1 billion to $65.6 billion.
